node_5.description: This is Tom Moreno's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am, open The Willow Market and Pharmacy at 8:00 am, help customers with their orders and manage store operations until closing at 6:00 pm, go home and have dinner with his wife at 6:30 pm, catch up on local news and updates on the upcoming election.
